00:20:44,014 --> 00:20:46,196
They're not lawyers like me who spend their days working

466
00:20:46,216 --> 00:20:46,857
on these issues.

467
00:20:47,218 --> 00:20:49,180
And that instead of getting this regulated,

468
00:20:49,340 --> 00:20:50,962
what we're going to get is all of this regulated.

